<li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">avez ou avez eu</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">une</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">convulsion</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">ou l'&eacute;pilepsie.</span></span></li>
